screen_desc: The screenshot shows the settings for "Events from Gmail" on a mobile device. It displays the email address linked to the account and offers toggles for syncing events, reminders, birthdays, and holidays. The options are divided into sections, with colored dots representing each category (purple for events, red for reminders, green for birthdays, and teal for holidays). Users can adjust these settings to manage notifications and sync preferences for different types of events linked to their Gmail account.
